        "email": "pfarrell@whamcloud.com",
        "username": "pfarrell",
        "inactive": true
      },
      "date": "2019-04-17 17:03:11.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 2:\n\nApologies for having so many of these on the go, but I put the reduced revert here:\nhttps://review.whamcloud.com/34699\n\nRather than replacing this change, so testing can continue here just in case the theory behind the 34699 change is incorrect.",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 2
    },
